:: reya-steel
@contact reya, phone-call
//@background
@trigger OnEnterEvidenceBoard
@when Seen(level03.dad-steamer)
@once

	$call TriggerConvoMusic(reya_convo)
	{@reya} Hey sis!
		Dad and I are going through the rest of Grandma's old stuff. 
		Check out this awesome postcard from Grandpa!
		What a legend. I bet his life was never boring. 
		{img postcard}
	{@you}   Wait a sec. Did you read this??
		It says the steel company sent Grandpa on an extra, unplanned trip.
	{@reya}  Um.... so? 
	{@you}   There weren't any official records of this.
	{@dad}   Wait a minute. You mean... I've been searching the wrong part of the lake??
	{@you}   Looks like it. 
		{/img}
	{@reya}  Yes!!! I found a clue! 
		Jules, you need to take your fancy research boat out there and check it out!
	{@you}  I still need to narrow down the location.
	{@reya}  Okay, okay. What are you waiting for? Make with the boring research! 
	{@you}   It's not boring, Reya. It's our history!
	{@reya}  Ha. Of course you would say that. 
	$call UnlockEvidence(4, "LV4-Card-Types")
	$call EndConvoMusic()


:: amy-lead
@contact amy, phone-call
@background amy-office
@trigger OnDialogClosed
@when Seen(level04.reya-steel)
@once

	$call TriggerConvoMusic(amy_convo)
	{@you}	Amy, I need your help. I found a new lead on Grandpa’s ship!
	{@amy}  You did?? I didn't know you were looking into it. 
	{@you}  Well.... my sister helped. A little. 
		[SEND MAP with new route added] 
		I marked my grandpa's route in blue.  
		He mentioned rough waves near the Apostle Islands. 
		Do you have any evidence of shipwrecks in that area? 
	{@amy}	Hmm, let’s see... 
		[Send image: piece of steel with OK Steel logo]
		A fisherman pulled up this broken piece of steel near Outer Island.  
		It could be from a freighter like your grandpa's!
		Location: 47°05'19.4"N 90°17'17.5"W
	{@you}	Thanks, Amy!
		I'll send the steel sample to my mom. 
		She can test it in her lab and find out more about it. 
	{@amy}	
	$call UnlockEvidence(4, "LV4-Location-Coordinates")
	$call RemoveEvidence(4, "LV4-Do-Later-Note")
	$call DiscoverLocation(4)
	$call EndConvoMusic()

